name: Swapped (Takeo Noname, Daigey, Luke's Jukebox, almaheart16)
name_original: Swapped (Takeo Noname, Daigey, Luke's Jukebox, almaheart16)
description: You just got a computer for your birthday, finally you can catch up with your friends in the comfort of your own home. You are excited to learn about what all you can do on the internet! Be careful though, some people know just what they can do on this platform and will take advantage of your ignorance. Chat with your buddy's, make new friends, and hide from the people who are trying to sell you on the dark web. Good Luck!
